Page.PageName: Steps 5-7 Alarm Test, Fault Function Test

Text.Value: To conduct a test of audible and visual alarm indicators, press and hold ALARM button at any time during the display sequence.
When "000" is displayed, check the proper operation of the buttons by pressing each and observing the numerical indication as shown:
• RATE (001)
• LIGHT (020)
• CLR/TEST (004)
Release the ALARM button and press the DOSE button. The DOSE ALARM light and sounder will turn on.
Release the DOSE button and press the RATE button. Only the RATE ALARM light and sounder will turn on.
